  	<p class="paragraph_intro">Increasingly, companies are choosing to plug-in to subscription services as a way of streamlining their IT management. Businesses are off-loading software maintenance and upgrades. They’re choosing to buy instead of build. This paradigm shift is known as Software as a Service or SaaS.</p>
