	<p>SaaS is a way to receive sophisticated functionality without needing to purchase or load traditional software applications onto PCs. It’s software that’s not tied to a specific device.</p>
	<p>These web applications are replacing the purchase of traditional software applications. For a monthly fee the costs can be kept low and consistent. SaaS can be personalized and upgraded to suit businesses of all sizes and types.</p>
	<p>Abletech can help you turn your SaaS idea into a reality.</p>
	<p>SaaS advantages:</p>
	<ul>
		<li>low barrier to adoption, you can try before you buy</li>
		<li>scales easily as your user base grows</li>
		<li>users always have the latest version</li>
